    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EPISODE 1: EAST WOOD CARNIVAL (Remake Coming Soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PlayStation One styled horror game made by a sixth grader. Your car runs out of gas on your way to an abandoned carnival now infested with danger at every corner. You have no friends, no hope, and are all alone in your endeavor for escape. This is a linear horror experience in which you will solve basic puzzles to escape the carnival, but don't forget that you are not alone. Keep a keen eye out for danger, it just might save your life. As you desperately try to escape you might just wonder why you wanted to come here in the first place. So are you up for the challenge? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WATCH YOUR BACK</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012820/extras/f2bb8f7991b11c6127daccdd7da88784.poster.avif?t=1761791677\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012820/extras/f2bb8f7991b11c6127daccdd7da88784.webm?t=1761791677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012820/extras/f2bb8f7991b11c6127daccdd7da88784.mp4?t=1761791677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>At every corner there is danger, so be careful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SOLVE PUZZLES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012820/extras/403570a8edcdd655b66314fb85465e18.poster.avif?t=1761791677\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012820/extras/403570a8edcdd655b66314fb85465e18.webm?t=1761791677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012820/extras/403570a8edcdd655b66314fb85465e18.mp4?t=1761791677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Flip levers to open doors and power up objects to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
